00:41:55.600 --> 00:41:59.070
But buffets better than afist of France:

761
00:41:59.070 --> 00:42:02.430
Zounds! I was never sobethump'd with words

762
00:42:02.430 --> 00:42:05.470
Since I first call'd mybrother's father dad.

763
00:42:07.200 --> 00:42:11.730
Son, list to thisconjunction, make this match;

764
00:42:11.730 --> 00:42:16.630
Give with our niece adowry large enough:

765
00:42:16.630 --> 00:42:19.130
For by this knot thoushalt so surely tie

766
00:42:19.130 --> 00:42:23.170
Thy now unsured assuranceto the crown,

