930
00:52:31.630 --> 00:52:43.970
Lewis marry Blanch! O boy,then where art thou?

931
00:52:44.970 --> 00:52:50.530
France friend with England,what becomes of me?

932
00:52:51.100 --> 00:52:53.700
Fellow, be gone: I cannotbrook thy sight:

933
00:52:53.700 --> 00:52:56.600
This news hath made thee amost ugly man.

934
00:52:56.600 --> 00:52:58.170
What other harm have I,good lady, done,

935
00:52:58.170 --> 00:53:00.170
