977
00:55:43.470 --> 00:55:46.730
The meagre cloddy earth toglittering gold:

978
00:55:46.730 --> 00:55:49.570
The yearly course thatbrings this day about

979
00:55:49.570 --> 00:55:52.330
Shall never see it but aholiday.

980
00:55:52.770 --> 00:55:56.000
A wicked day, and not aholy day!

981
00:55:56.000 --> 00:55:59.770
What hath this day deserved?what hath it done,

982
00:55:59.770 --> 00:56:01.670
That it in golden lettersshould be writ

983
00:56:01.670 --> 00:56:04.600
Among the high tides ofthe calendar?

984
00:56:04.600 --> 00:56:06.770
Nay, rather turn this dayout of the week,

985
00:56:06.770 --> 00:56:11.470
